Dialogue: 1,0:01:12.22,0:01:13.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,完美
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.22,0:01:13.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Perfect
Dialogue: 1,0:01:17.57,0:01:19.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,晚上好  邻居
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.57,0:01:19.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Evening, neighbor
Dialogue: 1,0:01:19.00,0:01:20.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,晚上好  普雷斯顿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.00,0:01:20.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Evening, Preston
Dialogue: 1,0:01:24.67,0:01:27.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,祝你今晚音乐会演出顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.67,0:01:27.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good luck at the concert tonight
Dialogue: 1,0:01:27.27,0:01:29.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢  塞巴斯蒂安
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.27,0:01:29.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Sebastian
Dialogue: 1,0:01:29.65,0:01:31.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们也许自以为认识我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.65,0:01:31.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You may think you know me
Dialogue: 1,0:01:31.34,0:01:32.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,其实不然
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.34,0:01:32.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but you don't
Dialogue: 1,0:01:32.48,0:01:35.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我曾经是章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.48,0:01:35.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I used to be Squidward Tentacles
Dialogue: 1,0:01:35.54,0:01:37.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而如今  我名叫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.54,0:01:37.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but now, the name's
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.74,0:01:39.87,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\an1\pos(1296,256)}今晚\N约翰海豚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.74,0:01:39.87,注释,,0,0,0,,[ 改自John Doe，指代身份不明的人 ]
Dialogue: 1,0:01:37.18,0:01:39.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海豚  约翰海豚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.18,0:01:39.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Dolphin, John Dolphin
Dialogue: 1,0:01:44.35,0:01:45.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是约翰海豚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.35,0:01:45.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's John Dolphin
Dialogue: 1,0:01:52.48,0:01:57.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在纽开普市拥有了美妙的新生活
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.48,0:01:57.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I have a wonderful new life in New Kelp City
Dialogue: 1,0:01:57.52,0:01:59.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,究竟怎么会这样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.52,0:01:59.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How did this happen?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:59.22,0:02:00.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,且听我分解
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.22,0:02:00.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll tell you
Dialogue: 1,0:02:01.27,0:02:04.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一天  我这辈子最糟糕的事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.27,0:02:04.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,One day, the worst thing that ever happened to me
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.18,0:02:08.73,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(986,344)}音乐
Dialogue: 1,0:02:04.76,0:02:05.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最终却变成了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.76,0:02:05.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,turned out to be
Dialogue: 1,0:02:05.92,0:02:08.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我这辈子最美好的事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.92,0:02:08.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the best thing that ever happened to me
Dialogue: 1,0:02:10.53,0:02:11.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.53,0:02:11.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Excuse me
Dialogue: 1,0:02:11.46,0:02:13.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要投诉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.46,0:02:13.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'd like to lodge a complaint
Dialogue: 1,0:02:13.12,0:02:15.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这簧片有毛病
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.12,0:02:15.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This reed is defective
Dialogue: 1,0:02:26.80,0:02:28.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.80,0:02:28.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:02:28.12,0:02:31.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们库存就只剩这片簧片了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.12,0:02:31.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but that's the only reed we have in stock
Dialogue: 1,0:02:31.00,0:02:33.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有没有考虑过演奏安全点的乐器
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.00,0:02:33.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Have you ever thought of playing something safer
Dialogue: 1,0:02:33.37,0:02:35.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,比如说三角铁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.37,0:02:35.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,like the triangle?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:37.49,0:02:38.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我这可是抢劫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.49,0:02:38.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is a stickup
Dialogue: 1,0:02:39.17,0:02:40.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把店里的钱全都交出来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.17,0:02:40.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Give me all the dough in the joint
Dialogue: 1,0:02:40.72,0:02:42.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不然我就擦掉你们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.72,0:02:42.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,or I'll rub you out
Dialogue: 1,0:02:43.47,0:02:45.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是埃莫橡皮擦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.47,0:02:45.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Elmer Eraser
Dialogue: 1,0:02:47.88,0:02:50.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是你们哪个白痴敢告密
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.88,0:02:50.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If either of you bozos squeal
Dialogue: 1,0:02:50.71,0:02:52.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我一定会找到你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.71,0:02:52.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll track ya down
Dialogue: 1,0:02:52.38,0:02:54.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把你给擦了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.38,0:02:54.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and rub you out
Dialogue: 1,0:02:58.53,0:03:00.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我一个字都不会说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.53,0:03:00.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I won't say a syllable
Dialogue: 1,0:03:01.20,0:03:05.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谅你也不敢  否则我一定会找到你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.20,0:03:05.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See that you don't, or Elmer Eraser will find you
Dialogue: 1,0:03:07.77,0:03:09.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,警察试图让我开口
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.77,0:03:09.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The police tried to get me to talk
Dialogue: 1,0:03:09.92,0:03:11.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然而我没兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.92,0:03:11.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but I wasn't interested
Dialogue: 1,0:03:11.90,0:03:13.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,至少起先如此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.90,0:03:13.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,at first
Dialogue: 1,0:03:14.11,0:03:16.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都说了  我什么都没看到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.11,0:03:16.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I told you, I didn't see a thing
Dialogue: 1,0:03:16.92,0:03:18.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放心  章鱼哥先生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.92,0:03:18.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not to worry, Mr. Tentacles
Dialogue: 1,0:03:18.90,0:03:20.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,如果你想起了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.90,0:03:20.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If you do remember anything
Dialogue: 1,0:03:20.47,0:03:23.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们可以把你纳入证人保护计划
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.47,0:03:23.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,we can put you into witness protection
Dialogue: 1,0:03:23.47,0:03:26.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当然  也只能把你搬到别处
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.47,0:03:26.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Of course, we'll have to move you to a new town
Dialogue: 1,0:03:26.05,0:03:28.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给你换个假名  安排新工作
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.05,0:03:28.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,change your name, and give you a new job
Dialogue: 1,0:03:28.64,0:03:31.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听好警官  我绝对不招
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.64,0:03:31.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look, officer, I'm not talking
Dialogue: 1,0:03:31.11,0:03:34.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可惜你就再也见不到你朋友跟邻居了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.11,0:03:32.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, you'll never see
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.44,0:03:34.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,your friends or neighbors again
Dialogue: 1,0:03:36.85,0:03:38.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我全都看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.85,0:03:38.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I saw everything
Dialogue: 1,0:03:38.42,0:03:40.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来作证
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.42,0:03:40.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll testify
Dialogue: 1,0:03:41.97,0:03:45.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,如今  我拥有了梦寐以求的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.97,0:03:45.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, I have everything I'd ever dreamed of
Dialogue: 1,0:03:56.09,0:03:58.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我一定是出幻觉了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.09,0:03:58.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I must be imagining things
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.75,0:03:59.09,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(606,356)}后台入口
Dialogue: 1,0:04:06.10,0:04:08.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不可能会有这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.10,0:04:08.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This can't be happening
Dialogue: 1,0:04:13.15,0:04:15.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们想你  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.15,0:04:15.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We miss you, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:04:24.61,0:04:26.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.61,0:04:26.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:04:37.76,0:04:38.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.76,0:04:38.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't worry
Dialogue: 1,0:04:38.55,0:04:39.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.55,0:04:39.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've got it
Dialogue: 1,0:04:39.61,0:04:40.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好爱你的新胡子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.61,0:04:40.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Love your new beard
Dialogue: 1,0:04:41.62,0:04:43.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢了  不过这胡子是假的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.62,0:04:43.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks, but it's only a fake one
Dialogue: 1,0:04:44.02,0:04:45.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝跟派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.02,0:04:45.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob and Patrick?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:45.80,0:04:48.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们俩白痴咋找到我的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.80,0:04:48.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How did you two goofballs find me?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:49.32,0:04:51.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想知道我们是咋找到你的吗  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.32,0:04:51.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You like to know how we found you, Squidward?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:53.68,0:04:55.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你声音从哪冒出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.68,0:04:55.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where's your voice coming from?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:55.16,0:04:57.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那是蟹堡王寻常的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.16,0:04:57.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It was an average day at the old Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:04:57.95,0:05:00.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但是某样东西失踪了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.95,0:05:00.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But something was missing
Dialogue: 1,0:05:00.34,0:05:02.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,或者应该说是  某个人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.34,0:05:02.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Or should I say "someone"?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:03.35,0:05:05.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.35,0:05:05.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:05.00,0:05:06.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,里面有人在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.00,0:05:06.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Anybody home?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:07.76,0:05:09.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊  这里的服务
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.76,0:05:09.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Boy, the service here
Dialogue: 1,0:05:09.09,0:05:12.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,越来越走下坡路了  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.09,0:05:12.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,is really going downhill, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:05:12.42,0:05:14.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥还没来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.42,0:05:14.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward's still not here?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:14.35,0:05:15.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来怪不得
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.35,0:05:15.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I guess that would explain
Dialogue: 1,0:05:15.35,0:05:17.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我好几周都没有收到点餐单
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.35,0:05:17.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,why I haven't had a single order in weeks
Dialogue: 1,0:05:17.82,0:05:21.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我也好几周都没见到他在家了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.82,0:05:21.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I haven't seen him in his house for weeks either
Dialogue: 1,0:05:21.13,0:05:23.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,更没见到他泡浴缸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.13,0:05:23.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,not even in his bathtub
Dialogue: 1,0:05:23.56,0:05:25.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且他冰箱也没吃的了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.56,0:05:25.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And his fridge is out of food
Dialogue: 1,0:05:25.90,0:05:28.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我真想我最爱的邻居
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.90,0:05:28.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I really miss my favorite neighbor
Dialogue: 1,0:05:28.67,0:05:30.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可我就在这啊  兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.67,0:05:30.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But I'm right here, buddy
Dialogue: 1,0:05:30.72,0:05:31.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢天谢地
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.72,0:05:31.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness
Dialogue: 1,0:05:31.92,0:05:34.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是要怎么找到章鱼哥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.92,0:05:34.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But how do we find Squidward?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:34.18,0:05:35.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.18,0:05:35.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't worry
Dialogue: 1,0:05:35.20,0:05:36.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.20,0:05:36.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got this
Dialogue: 1,0:05:42.00,0:05:45.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在只要有味道像章鱼哥的东西就行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.00,0:05:45.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, I just need something that smells like Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:05:46.83,0:05:48.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来片他的旧竖笛簧片应该可以
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.83,0:05:48.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,One of his old clarinet reeds should help
Dialogue: 1,0:05:53.76,0:05:54.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.76,0:05:54.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Got it
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.41,0:05:59.38,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(502,374)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:05:59.02,0:06:00.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,于是  我们跟着气味
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.02,0:06:00.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And so, we followed the scent
Dialogue: 1,0:06:00.79,0:06:02.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来到了你新家的大门
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.79,0:06:02.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to your new front door
Dialogue: 1,0:06:03.04,0:06:04.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为什么要离开我们  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.04,0:06:04.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why did you leave us, Squidward?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:05.38,0:06:08.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们两个傻子会全都搞砸的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.38,0:06:08.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You knuckleheads are gonna ruin everything
Dialogue: 1,0:06:08.09,0:06:10.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可是纳入了证人保护计划
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.09,0:06:10.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm in witness protection
Dialogue: 1,0:06:10.57,0:06:12.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,健身染毒计划
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.57,0:06:12.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fitness infection?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:12.47,0:06:15.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我这是在躲埃莫橡皮擦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.47,0:06:15.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm hiding out from Elmer Eraser
Dialogue: 1,0:06:15.96,0:06:17.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,埃莫橡皮擦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.96,0:06:17.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Elmer Eraser?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:17.76,0:06:20.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个爱擦告密者的抢匪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.76,0:06:20.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The robber who relishes in rubbing out rats?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:22.46,0:06:23.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们两个能不能快滚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.46,0:06:23.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Would you two get lost?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:23.95,0:06:26.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不然会引狼入室  害我被抓包
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.95,0:06:26.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're gonna lead that maniac right to me
Dialogue: 1,0:06:28.95,0:06:32.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我都不知道章鱼哥进了蠢人完护计划
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.95,0:06:32.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I had no idea Squidward was in witless perfection
Dialogue: 1,0:06:32.97,0:06:34.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,差点就害他暴露了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.97,0:06:34.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And we almost blew his cover
Dialogue: 1,0:06:36.15,0:06:37.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,刚刚真抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.15,0:06:37.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry about that
Dialogue: 1,0:06:37.58,0:06:38.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没看到你们在那
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.58,0:06:38.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I didn't see ya there
Dialogue: 1,0:06:38.97,0:06:41.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你那个橡皮擦挺好看的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.97,0:06:41.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Say, that sure is a nice eraser
Dialogue: 1,0:06:41.89,0:06:42.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.89,0:06:42.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks
Dialogue: 1,0:06:42.97,0:06:44.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我妈给我做的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.97,0:06:44.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My mommy made it for me
Dialogue: 1,0:06:46.39,0:06:48.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,橡皮擦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.39,0:06:48.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Eraser
Dialogue: 1,0:06:48.18,0:06:50.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让我想起来件事  是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.18,0:06:50.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That reminds me of something, but what?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:51.37,0:06:53.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们两个呆子知道要上哪去找
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.37,0:06:53.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do you bozos know where I can find
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.76,0:06:55.35,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1304,486)}关键证人
Dialogue: 1,0:06:54.33,0:06:55.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个笨蛋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.33,0:06:55.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,this mug?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:57.06,0:06:59.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,埃莫橡皮擦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.06,0:06:59.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Elmer Eraser?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:59.65,0:07:00.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那不是杯子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.65,0:07:00.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's not a mug
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.65,0:07:00.72,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(1056,920)}笨 蛋
Dialogue: 1,0:07:00.72,0:07:01.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.72,0:07:01.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's
Dialogue: 1,0:07:01.12,0:07:03.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们这辈子从来没见过那位
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.12,0:07:03.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We've never seen that person in our entire lives
Dialogue: 1,0:07:04.04,0:07:05.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不管他长没长胡子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.04,0:07:05.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,with or without a beard
Dialogue: 1,0:07:05.81,0:07:07.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是你们见过
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.81,0:07:07.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, if you do
Dialogue: 1,0:07:10.28,0:07:11.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就麻烦你们告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.28,0:07:11.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,please let me know
Dialogue: 1,0:07:13.51,0:07:16.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  那个就是埃莫橡皮擦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.51,0:07:16.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, that was Elmer Eraser
Dialogue: 1,0:07:16.26,0:07:17.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.26,0:07:17.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:17.10,0:07:18.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,必须警告章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.10,0:07:18.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We gotta warn Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:07:20.11,0:07:23.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,感谢海神王  那俩白痴走了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.11,0:07:23.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank Neptune those idiots are gone
Dialogue: 1,0:07:23.35,0:07:24.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.35,0:07:24.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:07:26.53,0:07:27.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,结果又回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.53,0:07:27.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And they're back
Dialogue: 1,0:07:27.72,0:07:29.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,猜猜我们在外面看到谁了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.72,0:07:29.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Guess who we saw outside?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:29.50,0:07:31.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,埃莫橡皮擦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.50,0:07:31.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Elmer Eraser
Dialogue: 1,0:07:31.17,0:07:32.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.17,0:07:32.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:32.44,0:07:33.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.44,0:07:33.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm doomed
Dialogue: 1,0:07:33.78,0:07:34.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.78,0:07:34.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't worry
Dialogue: 1,0:07:34.57,0:07:37.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们要把你纳入证人保护保护计划
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.57,0:07:37.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We'll put you into witness protection protection
Dialogue: 1,0:07:37.67,0:07:39.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你有我们保护很安全
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.67,0:07:39.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're safe with us
Dialogue: 1,0:07:41.95,0:07:44.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这边这个藏身处有很多自然光
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.95,0:07:44.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here's a hideout with a lot of natural light
Dialogue: 1,0:07:47.38,0:07:48.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,玻璃屋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.38,0:07:48.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A glass house?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:48.61,0:07:50.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们疯了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.61,0:07:50.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you nuts?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:50.27,0:07:52.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样就看得到埃莫橡皮擦过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.27,0:07:52.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This way, you can see Elmer Eraser coming
Dialogue: 1,0:07:52.92,0:07:55.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可他也看得到我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.92,0:07:55.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But he can see me too
Dialogue: 1,0:07:55.74,0:07:56.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.74,0:07:56.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You
Dialogue: 1,0:07:56.87,0:07:58.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们骗了我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.87,0:07:58.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You guys lied to me
Dialogue: 1,0:07:58.83,0:08:00.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就是章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.83,0:08:00.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:08:02.02,0:08:02.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.02,0:08:02.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't worry
Dialogue: 1,0:08:02.91,0:08:04.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来解决他
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.91,0:08:04.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got him
Dialogue: 1,0:08:04.21,0:08:04.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.21,0:08:04.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 1,0:08:04.71,0:08:05.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.71,0:08:05.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't
Dialogue: 1,0:08:09.38,0:08:12.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,原来这是有机玻璃屋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.38,0:08:12.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's a plexiglass house
Dialogue: 1,0:08:16.78,0:08:17.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,完美
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.78,0:08:17.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Perfect
Dialogue: 1,0:08:17.72,0:08:19.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们可以开得远远的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.72,0:08:19.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We can drive far, far away
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.43,0:08:23.89,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1218,718)}垃圾场
Dialogue: 1,0:08:24.20,0:08:25.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抓到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.20,0:08:25.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gotcha
Dialogue: 1,0:08:26.06,0:08:27.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家跳船啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.06,0:08:27.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Everybody jump
Dialogue: 1,0:08:30.14,0:08:32.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样逃脱才对嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.14,0:08:32.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is how you make a getaway
Dialogue: 1,0:08:33.19,0:08:33.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.19,0:08:33.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 1,0:08:43.08,0:08:43.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.08,0:08:43.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Quick
Dialogue: 1,0:08:43.75,0:08:44.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,进去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.75,0:08:44.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,In there
Dialogue: 1,0:08:57.31,0:08:58.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,爬上去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.31,0:08:58.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Up there
Dialogue: 1,0:09:15.55,0:09:16.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你在这里就安全了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.55,0:09:16.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You'll be safe in here
Dialogue: 1,0:09:21.31,0:09:22.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抓到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.31,0:09:22.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gotcha
Dialogue: 1,0:09:31.17,0:09:33.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥没了保护
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.17,0:09:33.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward is unprotected
Dialogue: 1,0:09:33.72,0:09:34.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.72,0:09:34.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hop on
Dialogue: 1,0:09:43.45,0:09:45.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们会救你的  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.45,0:09:45.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We'll save you, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:09:58.55,0:09:59.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.55,0:09:59.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no
Dialogue: 1,0:09:59.88,0:10:02.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那两个白痴找到我了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.88,0:10:02.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Those two halfwits found me
Dialogue: 1,0:10:07.50,0:10:09.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,原来只是埃莫橡皮擦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.50,0:10:09.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's just Elmer Eraser
Dialogue: 1,0:10:10.92,0:10:13.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,埃莫橡皮擦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.92,0:10:13.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Elmer Eraser
Dialogue: 1,0:10:15.17,0:10:17.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们会保护你的  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.17,0:10:17.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We'll protect you, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:10:17.19,0:10:18.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抓到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.19,0:10:18.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gotcha
Dialogue: 1,0:10:18.81,0:10:20.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,求你了  埃莫橡皮擦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.81,0:10:20.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please, Elmer Eraser
Dialogue: 1,0:10:20.47,0:10:22.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别把章鱼哥擦了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.47,0:10:22.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,don't rub out Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:10:23.91,0:10:24.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.91,0:10:24.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't worry
Dialogue: 1,0:10:24.90,0:10:26.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不是埃莫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.90,0:10:26.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm not Elmer
Dialogue: 1,0:10:26.28,0:10:28.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是侦探橡皮擦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.28,0:10:28.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm Detective Eraser
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.81,0:10:28.64,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1012,300)}裤头村警察局
Dialogue: 1,0:10:31.77,0:10:33.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,埃莫是我的双胞胎兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.77,0:10:33.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Elmer's my twin brother
Dialogue: 1,0:10:33.87,0:10:35.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我整天都在找你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.87,0:10:35.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've been trying to find you all day
Dialogue: 1,0:10:36.50,0:10:37.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢天谢地
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.50,0:10:37.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness
Dialogue: 1,0:10:37.78,0:10:40.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你能不能逮捕那两个傻子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.78,0:10:40.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can you arrest these two blockheads
Dialogue: 1,0:10:40.20,0:10:42.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让我继续过上约翰海豚的美好生活
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.20,0:10:42.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so I can go back to being John Dolphin?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:42.65,0:10:43.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,告诉你个好消息
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.65,0:10:43.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Lucky for you
Dialogue: 1,0:10:43.70,0:10:46.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我兄弟埃莫已经被抓去坐牢了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.70,0:10:46.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,my brother Elmer has been caught and put in jail
Dialogue: 1,0:10:46.80,0:10:49.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你再也不需要证人保护计划了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.80,0:10:49.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You don't need witness protection anymore
Dialogue: 1,0:10:54.42,0:10:56.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是不是很棒  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.42,0:10:56.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Isn't it great, Squidward?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:56.22,0:10:59.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你可以回裤头村陪我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.22,0:10:59.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can come back to Bikini Bottom with us
Dialogue: 1,0:10:59.28,0:11:01.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.28,0:11:01.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward's back
Dialogue: 1,0:11:01.61,0:11:03.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.61,0:11:03.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wonderful
Dialogue: 1,0:11:03.07,0:11:04.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.07,0:11:04.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward's back
Dialogue: 1,0:11:06.87,0:11:07.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你当鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.87,0:11:07.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're it
Dialogue: 1,0:11:07.52,0:11:08.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  你当鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.52,0:11:08.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, you're it
Dialogue: 1,0:11:08.70,0:11:09.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  你当鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.70,0:11:09.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, you're it
Dialogue: 1,0:11:09.39,0:11:10.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥当鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.39,0:11:10.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward's it
Dialogue: 1,0:11:10.27,0:11:10.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  你当鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.27,0:11:10.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, you're it
Dialogue: 1,0:11:11.20,0:11:13.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我总算安全了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.20,0:11:13.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I was finally safe
Dialogue: 1,0:11:13.44,0:11:17.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但我即将目击又一桩罪案
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.44,0:11:17.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but I was about to become witness to another crime
Dialogue: 1,0:11:17.82,0:11:21.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一桩我即将犯下的罪案
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.82,0:11:21.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,a crime I was going to commit
Dialogue: 1,0:11:21.32,0:11:23.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要把你们都擦了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.32,0:11:23.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm going to rub you out
Dialogue: 1,0:11:29.79,0:11:31.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,擦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.79,0:11:31.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Rub
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.09,0:11:37.67,起司 特殊标题,,0,0,0,,树屋隔离
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.88,0:11:39.09,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(716,406)}编剧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.88,0:11:39.09,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(734,698)}分镜总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.88,0:11:43.39,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1530,976.667)}翻译{\fnArial}: 1440kHz
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.30,0:11:40.51,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(578,476)}指导总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.30,0:11:40.51,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(750,692)}动画总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.76,0:11:41.97,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(740,548)}统筹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.22,0:11:43.39,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(596,560)}监制
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.68,0:11:45.14,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(640,598)}监制
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.68,0:11:45.14,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1468.667,976.667)}本字幕仅限学习交流\N严禁用于商业用途
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.22,0:11:47.64,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1142,578)}坚果谷仓
Dialogue: 1,0:11:47.22,0:11:51.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊  刚刚在坚果谷仓好个大买特买
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.22,0:11:49.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Boy, that was one heck of a shoppin' spree
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.85,0:11:51.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,down at the old Nut Barn
Dialogue: 1,0:11:57.93,0:11:58.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过很值得
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.93,0:11:58.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Worth it, though
Dialogue: 1,0:12:00.50,0:12:02.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嘎嘣脆的坚果真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.50,0:12:02.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,These cracklin' nuts taste so good
Dialogue: 1,0:12:02.58,0:12:05.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就好像我嘴里开了个民歌演唱会似的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.58,0:12:05.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it's like there's a hootenanny in my mouth
Dialogue: 1,0:12:14.59,0:12:15.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那玩意哪来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.59,0:12:15.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where'd that come fr
Dialogue: 1,0:12:17.70,0:12:19.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我头盔就快跟鸡蛋似的碎掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.70,0:12:19.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My helmet's about to crack like an egg
Dialogue: 1,0:12:20.23,0:12:22.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,必须尽快回树屋里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.23,0:12:22.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I gotta get home to my dome ASAP
Dialogue: 1,0:12:28.57,0:12:30.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,刚刚真是好险啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.57,0:12:30.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That was a close shave
Dialogue: 1,0:12:30.60,0:12:32.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最好找出我的备用头盔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.60,0:12:32.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Better dig out my backup helmet
Dialogue: 1,0:12:37.15,0:12:39.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定是我手指沾到的坚果灰害的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.15,0:12:39.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Must be all that nut dust on my fingers
Dialogue: 1,0:12:39.83,0:12:42.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来我一个头盔都不剩了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.83,0:12:42.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Looks like I'm plumb out of helmets
Dialogue: 1,0:12:42.42,0:12:44.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最好去订购个新的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.42,0:12:44.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Better order a new one
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.07,0:12:45.03,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1194,370)}头盔专线
Dialogue: 1,0:12:47.93,0:12:48.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.93,0:12:48.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:48.70,0:12:49.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,头盔专线吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.70,0:12:49.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Helmets Direct?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:49.85,0:12:51.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  我要再买一个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.85,0:12:51.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I need another one
Dialogue: 1,0:12:51.65,0:12:52.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要多大的尺寸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.65,0:12:52.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What size do you need?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:52.58,0:12:53.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,尺寸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.58,0:12:53.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Size?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:53.60,0:12:54.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,尺寸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.60,0:12:54.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Size?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:54.44,0:12:55.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,松鼠中号
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.44,0:12:55.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squirrel medium
Dialogue: 1,0:12:55.54,0:12:56.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们中号卖光了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.54,0:12:56.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're out of size medium
Dialogue: 1,0:12:57.35,0:12:58.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只能特别定制
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.35,0:12:58.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll have to special order it
Dialogue: 1,0:12:58.95,0:13:00.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,得要六到八周才能送达
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.95,0:13:00.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's gonna take six to eight weeks to get it
Dialogue: 1,0:13:00.70,0:13:02.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,六到八周吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.70,0:13:02.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Six to eight weeks?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:03.60,0:13:05.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来我只能困在这里一阵子了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.60,0:13:05.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Looks like I'm stuck inside for a while
Dialogue: 1,0:13:05.97,0:13:08.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过能做的事有不少呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.97,0:13:08.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But I got plenty to do
Dialogue: 1,0:13:47.82,0:13:50.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,才过了一小时
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.82,0:13:50.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's only been one hour
Dialogue: 1,0:13:50.20,0:13:52.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就已经受不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.20,0:13:52.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but I can't take it anymore
Dialogue: 1,0:13:53.12,0:13:55.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是再看不到一只活物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.12,0:13:55.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If I don't see another living critter soon
Dialogue: 1,0:13:56.19,0:13:58.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就要疯了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.19,0:13:58.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna go nuts
Dialogue: 1,0:13:59.73,0:14:00.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,疯了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.73,0:14:00.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nuts
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.73,0:14:00.40,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(958,920)}坚 果
Dialogue: 1,0:14:02.15,0:14:03.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没事  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.15,0:14:03.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, now, Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:14:03.65,0:14:05.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你不会疯的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.65,0:14:05.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You'd never go nuts
Dialogue: 1,0:14:05.35,0:14:08.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你可是牢牢把握着现实呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.35,0:14:08.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your grip on reality is too firm
Dialogue: 1,0:14:09.11,0:14:11.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢了  坚果兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.11,0:14:11.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Nutty Buddy
Dialogue: 1,0:14:11.08,0:14:13.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你总能在我身边挺我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.08,0:14:13.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're always here for me
Dialogue: 1,0:14:13.53,0:14:15.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,朋友就该互帮互助
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.53,0:14:15.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's what friends are for
Dialogue: 1,0:14:15.22,0:14:17.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也许我可以把谁给套过来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.22,0:14:17.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe I can lasso someone into coming over
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.50,0:14:23.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,75,,发出很多邀请后
Dialogue: 1,0:14:23.09,0:14:24.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就不懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.09,0:14:24.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't understand
Dialogue: 1,0:14:24.90,0:14:28.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么个个周二下午两点半都没空
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.90,0:14:28.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How can everyone be busy at 2:30 on a Tuesday?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:30.93,0:14:32.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.93,0:14:32.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know
Dialogue: 1,0:14:32.01,0:14:34.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是我没办法让朋友来看望我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.01,0:14:34.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If I can't get my friends to visit me
Dialogue: 1,0:14:34.57,0:14:35.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就自己看望他们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.57,0:14:35.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll visit them
Dialogue: 1,0:14:36.29,0:14:37.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,远程看望
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.29,0:14:37.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,remotely
Dialogue: 1,0:14:56.01,0:14:56.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你能行的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.01,0:14:56.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You got this
Dialogue: 1,0:14:57.46,0:14:58.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你行的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.46,0:14:58.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You got it
Dialogue: 1,0:14:59.33,0:15:03.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,简直是刺激得不得了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.33,0:15:03.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, that's about as exciting as riding a no-legged bull
Dialogue: 1,0:15:03.07,0:15:04.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,下一个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.07,0:15:04.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Next
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.88,0:15:19.48,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(540,740)}墙
Dialogue: 1,0:15:10.43,0:15:11.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,非常好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.43,0:15:11.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Very good
Dialogue: 1,0:15:11.67,0:15:14.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在试试看侧方停船
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.67,0:15:14.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, let's try parallel parking
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.94,0:15:34.03,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1616,942)}救生员
Dialogue: 1,0:15:24.17,0:15:25.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,举
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.17,0:15:25.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And
Dialogue: 1,0:15:26.00,0:15:26.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,完了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.00,0:15:26.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,done
Dialogue: 1,0:15:26.78,0:15:29.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在换这只手举一万下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.78,0:15:29.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, for 10,000 with this arm
Dialogue: 1,0:15:29.66,0:15:31.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.66,0:15:31.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,One
