Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.67,0:15:34.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Two
Dialogue: 1,0:15:35.55,0:15:37.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,三
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.55,0:15:37.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Three
Dialogue: 1,0:15:39.67,0:15:41.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,简直害得我眼皮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.67,0:15:41.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is making my eyelids
Dialogue: 1,0:15:41.36,0:15:43.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,比拉里的杠铃还难抬
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.36,0:15:43.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,feel heavier than Larry's weights
Dialogue: 1,0:15:43.63,0:15:44.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,下一个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.63,0:15:44.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Next
Dialogue: 1,0:15:54.07,0:15:55.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,数完了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.07,0:15:55.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And done
Dialogue: 1,0:15:57.15,0:15:59.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在换这只手数一万张
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.15,0:15:59.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now for 10,000 with this arm
Dialogue: 1,0:16:00.27,0:16:02.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.27,0:16:02.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,One
Dialogue: 1,0:16:03.17,0:16:04.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,二
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.17,0:16:04.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Two
Dialogue: 1,0:16:06.08,0:16:08.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,三
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.08,0:16:08.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Three
Dialogue: 1,0:16:10.10,0:16:11.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,四
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.10,0:16:11.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Four
Dialogue: 1,0:16:14.16,0:16:16.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,五
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.16,0:16:16.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Five
Dialogue: 1,0:16:19.19,0:16:22.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,裤头村里肯定有什么趣事可以看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.19,0:16:21.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's gotta be something interesting
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.29,0:16:22.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to look at in this town
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.62,0:16:20.66,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(634,214)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:16:24.94,0:16:26.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.94,0:16:26.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What in the?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:26.72,0:16:27.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,果不其然
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.72,0:16:27.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Of course
Dialogue: 1,0:16:28.32,0:16:30.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是我先前撞到的那个巨大金属玩意
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.32,0:16:30.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That big old metal whatsit I ran into
Dialogue: 1,0:16:31.50,0:16:32.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.50,0:16:32.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Plankton?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:32.84,0:16:35.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最好凑近一点看看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.84,0:16:35.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Better go in for a closer look
Dialogue: 1,0:16:37.95,0:16:39.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么声音这么吵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.95,0:16:39.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's that noise?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:40.52,0:16:42.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不会又一整晚没关凯伦了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.52,0:16:42.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Did I leave Karen on all night again?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:50.27,0:16:53.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今年的蚊子真是越来越大了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.27,0:16:53.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mosquitos sure are getting big this year
Dialogue: 1,0:16:57.49,0:16:58.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可恶的痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.49,0:16:58.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Dang that Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:16:59.29,0:17:02.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我得查清楚他有什么打算
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.29,0:17:02.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now I gotta figure out what he's up to
Dialogue: 1,0:17:05.04,0:17:05.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.04,0:17:05.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yello?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:06.12,0:17:07.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,喂  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.12,0:17:07.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Heya, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:17:07.76,0:17:10.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我手头上有一点调查的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.76,0:17:10.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm in the middle of an investigation
Dialogue: 1,0:17:10.14,0:17:13.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,希望你可以帮我稍微侦察一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.14,0:17:11.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and I was hoping you could do
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.67,0:17:13.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,a little reconnoitering for me
Dialogue: 1,0:17:15.76,0:17:16.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.76,0:17:16.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gosh, Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:17:16.41,0:17:17.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,虽然我很愿意
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.41,0:17:17.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'd love to
Dialogue: 1,0:17:17.19,0:17:21.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但我已经在帮蟹老板侦察新芥末矿了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.19,0:17:19.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but I'm already reconnoitering
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.22,0:17:21.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,a new mustard mine for Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:17:30.31,0:17:31.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我懂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.31,0:17:31.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I get it
Dialogue: 1,0:17:31.17,0:17:31.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我懂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.17,0:17:31.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I get it
Dialogue: 1,0:17:31.81,0:17:32.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你没空
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.81,0:17:32.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're busy
Dialogue: 1,0:17:32.80,0:17:34.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这种事没必要大吼大叫
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.80,0:17:34.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You don't have to holler about it
Dialogue: 1,0:17:43.20,0:17:44.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.20,0:17:44.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:44.35,0:17:45.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,喂  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.35,0:17:45.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Howdy, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:17:45.31,0:17:47.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要偷窥痞老板的诡计
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.31,0:17:47.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm trying to peep Plankton's plans
Dialogue: 1,0:17:47.58,0:17:48.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能来帮忙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.58,0:17:48.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wanna help out?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:48.89,0:17:49.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.89,0:17:49.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sure
Dialogue: 1,0:17:49.93,0:17:53.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等我吃完三明治就来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.93,0:17:53.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll be over as soon as I finish my sandwich
Dialogue: 1,0:17:54.32,0:17:55.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.32,0:17:55.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 1,0:17:58.75,0:17:59.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.75,0:17:59.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:17:59.94,0:18:01.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这任务应该够简单了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.94,0:18:01.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This should be simple enough
Dialogue: 1,0:18:02.47,0:18:04.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,痞老板在建造某种邪恶装置
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.47,0:18:04.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Plankton is building some sort of evil device
Dialogue: 1,0:18:04.64,0:18:07.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你就只要带着我的摄像机过去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.64,0:18:07.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All you gotta do is head over there with my camera
Dialogue: 1,0:18:07.64,0:18:08.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后看一眼就行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.64,0:18:08.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and give it a look 'fer
Dialogue: 1,0:18:08.79,0:18:09.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有没有收到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.79,0:18:09.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Roger?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:09.44,0:18:10.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看一眼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.44,0:18:10.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A look 'fer
Dialogue: 1,0:18:10.80,0:18:11.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,收到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.80,0:18:11.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Roger
Dialogue: 1,0:18:20.55,0:18:21.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你这是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.55,0:18:21.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Whatcha
Dialogue: 1,0:18:22.40,0:18:24.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在干什么  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.40,0:18:24.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,doin' there, Patrick?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:24.55,0:18:27.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在找罗杰
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.55,0:18:27.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Looking for Roger
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.55,0:18:27.57,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(1026,920)}收 到
Dialogue: 1,0:18:28.60,0:18:29.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我给你帮一把得了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.60,0:18:29.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let me give you a little help
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.17,0:18:34.67,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(976,448)}海之霸
Dialogue: 1,0:18:42.03,0:18:46.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,凯伦  我去买咖啡跟油煎饼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.03,0:18:46.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Karen, I'm going out for coffee and crullers
Dialogue: 1,0:18:46.98,0:18:47.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,正好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.98,0:18:47.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Perfect
Dialogue: 1,0:18:47.87,0:18:50.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,趁痞老板不在  四处张望
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.87,0:18:50.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Snoop around while Plankton's gone
Dialogue: 1,0:18:50.10,0:18:51.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.10,0:18:51.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:18:51.22,0:18:52.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就爱张望
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.22,0:18:52.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I love snooping
Dialogue: 1,0:18:52.95,0:18:56.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,张望张望张张望望
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.95,0:18:56.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Snoop, snoop, snooper snoop, snoopy snoop
Dialogue: 1,0:18:56.47,0:18:57.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,张大眼睛找线索
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.47,0:18:57.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Keep your eyes peeled for a clue
Dialogue: 1,0:18:57.91,0:18:59.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,用它看出来痞老板有什么打算
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.91,0:18:59.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that might tell us what he's up to
Dialogue: 1,0:18:59.97,0:19:01.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蓝图  存储卡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.97,0:19:01.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Blueprints, memory cards
Dialogue: 1,0:19:01.84,0:19:02.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,微缩胶片
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.84,0:19:02.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,microfiche
Dialogue: 1,0:19:02.55,0:19:03.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我找到东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.55,0:19:03.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I found something
Dialogue: 1,0:19:03.91,0:19:04.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是不是线索
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.91,0:19:04.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is it a clue?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:04.81,0:19:05.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.81,0:19:05.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:19:05.99,0:19:08.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还可好吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.99,0:19:08.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A delicious one
Dialogue: 1,0:19:08.16,0:19:10.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是他午饭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.16,0:19:10.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's his lunch
Dialogue: 1,0:19:15.34,0:19:16.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  那不是线索
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.34,0:19:16.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, that ain't a clue
Dialogue: 1,0:19:16.52,0:19:18.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是个小卷饼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.52,0:19:18.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's a tiny burrito
Dialogue: 1,0:19:18.17,0:19:20.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好好好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.17,0:19:20.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay
Dialogue: 1,0:19:25.02,0:19:27.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快来  罗杰罗杰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.02,0:19:27.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here, Roger, Roger
Dialogue: 1,0:19:29.20,0:19:30.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,根本就没东西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.20,0:19:30.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's nothing here
Dialogue: 1,0:19:30.65,0:19:32.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只有这一整个破盒子的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.65,0:19:32.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just this dumb old box of
Dialogue: 1,0:19:33.85,0:19:36.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,金不木奉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.85,0:19:36.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"puh-loo-toe-ni-um"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.48,0:19:36.11,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1008,468)}钚棒
Dialogue: 1,0:19:36.90,0:19:37.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,管他呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.90,0:19:37.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who cares?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:38.78,0:19:40.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,钚棒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.78,0:19:40.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Plutonium?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:40.78,0:19:43.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,痞老板一定是在建造某种核武器
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.78,0:19:43.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Plankton must be building some sort of atomic weapon
Dialogue: 1,0:19:45.20,0:19:47.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且还剑指蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.20,0:19:47.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And it's pointed right at the Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.70,0:19:48.20,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(418,284)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:19:48.52,0:19:50.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  你的使命完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.52,0:19:50.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, Patrick, you've done your part
Dialogue: 1,0:19:50.31,0:19:53.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这些荧光棒害我骨头痒死了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.31,0:19:53.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,These glow sticks make my bones itchy
Dialogue: 1,0:19:53.97,0:19:56.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我现在要用激光射他
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.97,0:19:56.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now I'm gonna zap him with my laser
Dialogue: 1,0:19:56.97,0:19:59.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先预热一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.97,0:19:59.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,She's warming up now
Dialogue: 1,0:20:00.72,0:20:01.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.72,0:20:01.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no
Dialogue: 1,0:20:01.91,0:20:03.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,痞老板回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.91,0:20:03.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Plankton's back
Dialogue: 1,0:20:03.13,0:20:05.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  快撤啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.13,0:20:05.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, you gotta get outta there
Dialogue: 1,0:20:05.05,0:20:06.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别被他给看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.05,0:20:06.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't let him see you
Dialogue: 1,0:20:06.75,0:20:08.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.75,0:20:08.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hurry
Dialogue: 1,0:20:08.00,0:20:10.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要迎风而上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.00,0:20:10.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am like unto the wind
Dialogue: 1,0:20:23.72,0:20:25.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你来这干什么  白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.72,0:20:25.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here, bozo?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:25.73,0:20:27.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我名字叫派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.73,0:20:27.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My name's Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:20:27.34,0:20:28.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不叫白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.34,0:20:28.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,not Bozo
Dialogue: 1,0:20:29.31,0:20:30.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,废话  大侦探
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.31,0:20:30.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, no duh, Sherlock
Dialogue: 1,0:20:30.91,0:20:34.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我名字叫白痴  不叫大侦探
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.91,0:20:34.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My name's Bozo, not Sherlock
Dialogue: 1,0:20:35.84,0:20:37.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.84,0:20:37.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no
Dialogue: 1,0:20:37.20,0:20:38.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,被他发现了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.20,0:20:38.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's onto us
Dialogue: 1,0:20:38.62,0:20:40.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,该亮出武器了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.62,0:20:40.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Time to take out that weapon
Dialogue: 1,0:20:43.40,0:20:45.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我知道你名字  笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.40,0:20:45.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know your name, ding dong
Dialogue: 1,0:20:46.05,0:20:49.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我名字叫大侦探  不叫笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.05,0:20:49.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My name's Sherlock, not Ding Dong
Dialogue: 1,0:20:49.43,0:20:50.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,够了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.43,0:20:50.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Enough
Dialogue: 1,0:20:50.57,0:20:51.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.57,0:20:51.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter
Dialogue: 1,0:20:51.70,0:20:56.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就让你第一个见证我的邪恶新发明
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.70,0:20:53.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're gonna be the first
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.23,0:20:56.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to witness my latest evil invention
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.82,0:21:04.74,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(704,342)}快来海之霸用餐
Dialogue: 1,0:21:05.11,0:21:07.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快来海之霸用餐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.11,0:21:07.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Eat at the Chum Bucket"
Dialogue: 1,0:21:07.67,0:21:10.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就只是个破广告牌吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.67,0:21:10.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's just a dumb, old sign?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:10.82,0:21:12.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,才不邪恶呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.82,0:21:12.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's not evil
Dialogue: 1,0:21:13.25,0:21:16.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,钚棒的来源不怎么符合道德标准
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.25,0:21:16.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, the plutonium wasn't sourced ethically
Dialogue: 1,0:21:16.75,0:21:18.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,算是有点邪恶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.75,0:21:18.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so it's a little evil
Dialogue: 1,0:21:25.81,0:21:26.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.81,0:21:26.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Boy
Dialogue: 1,0:21:34.05,0:21:35.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我怎么没想到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.05,0:21:35.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why didn't I think of that?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:35.97,0:21:37.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看招  老螃蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.97,0:21:37.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Eat that, Krabs
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.56,0:21:42.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,75,,六到八周后
Dialogue: 1,0:21:42.69,0:21:44.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢你帮我开餐厅
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.69,0:21:44.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks for hosting me restaurant
Dialogue: 1,0:21:44.33,0:21:46.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,毕竟蟹堡王坏了  还在维修
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.33,0:21:46.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,while the Krusty Krab is being repaired
Dialogue: 1,0:21:47.08,0:21:51.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝又被大猩猩弄伤  还在休养
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.08,0:21:49.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and while SpongeBob's recovering
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.03,0:21:51.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,from his gorilla injuries
Dialogue: 1,0:21:51.12,0:21:53.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,尽一点绵薄之力而已
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.12,0:21:53.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's the least I could do
Dialogue: 1,0:21:55.46,0:21:56.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的头盔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.46,0:21:56.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My helmet
Dialogue: 1,0:21:56.76,0:21:57.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,终于来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.76,0:21:57.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Finally
Dialogue: 1,0:22:00.42,0:22:02.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的新餐厅
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.42,0:22:02.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Me new restaurant
Dialogue: 1,0:22:02.70,0:22:04.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,终于来了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.70,0:22:04.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Finally
Dialogue: 1,0:22:04.32,0:22:06.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别闲逛了  章鱼哥先生
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.32,0:22:06.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Quit yer loafin', Mr. Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:22:06.13,0:22:08.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快去搬蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.13,0:22:08.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ya got a buildin' to move
Dialogue: 1,0:22:12.40,0:22:16.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还要再待树屋里六到八周吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.40,0:22:16.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Six to eight more weeks on the inside?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:21.49,0:22:24.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你要不要来接下一班啊  坚果兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.49,0:22:24.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How-how about you take the next shift, Nutty Buddy?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:29.04,0:22:32.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊  我得交点新朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.04,0:22:32.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Man, I gotta make some new friends
